title: John Keel - The Mothman Prophecies
description:
Not many people are aware that the Mothman encounters in Point Pleasant during the 1960&#039;s were not the main event.

John Keel shows in his book, The Mothman Prophecies, that UFO&#039;s, strange phone calls, mysterious indigenous people predicting events that never occurred, and mysterious people dressed in black (also known as the "Men in Black") haunted the small town.

Keel describes how names and numbers play a much bigger role in the mystery - a mystery that has been with humans since before recorded history.

The movie is just a small bacteria on the surface on a mystery as big as the universe.
